org.jirduino.translators

Class SignalRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jirduino.translators.SignalRule

  • public class SignalRule
extends java.lang.Object
    Signals Rule item, a SignalRule object will be stored into Signal Rules Table. It contains input/output signals and attributes like delay time (to wait before send output signal) and enable/disable sending flag. Rule fields: 
         --------------------------------------
    | IN   |   OUT   |  DELAY  |  ENABLED  |
     --------------------------------------
    • IN: Input Signal
    • OUT: Output Signal
    • DELAY: Delay time (in millis) to wait before sending (by Arduino) output signal
    • ENABLED: if false, output signal won't be sent by Arduino.
    Author:
    Emanuele Paiano
    See Also:
